content:
@Saul Kravitz Can you confirm that the search parameter on InsurancePlan - identifier - has been intentionally removed?
We saw this on earlier versions of the IG and anticipated our consumers would be using this as primary way to identify a member's network (tied to their plan code).
It was listed in these versions:
https://build.fhir.org/ig/HL7/davinci-pdex-plan-net/branches/mitre_v1/searchparameters.html
https://build.fhir.org/ig/HL7/davinci-pdex-plan-net/branches/fsh_april_2020/searchParameters.html
image.png

But it is not in the current version (and looks to have been removed with the v0.1.4 branch.
image.png

Thanks as always for your help!
cc: @Bapi Behera , @Mona O, @Annette Kuball

We made a lot of cuts, but that one was dropped inadvertently.
Will be in the STU1. See https://build.fhir.org/ig/HL7/davinci-pdex-plan-net/branches/v0.1.8/SearchParameter-insuranceplan-identifier.html
